verses.1: Topa phat un. Ama biakinn sungah Pasian phat unla, ama vangliatna mun vantungah amah phat un.
verses.2: A vanglian ama sepnate hangin amah phat unla, a liat mahmahna tawh kituakin amah phat un.
verses.3: Peengkul aw tawh amah phat unla, githa lasakna le harp lasakna tawh amah phat un.
verses.4: Khuang le lamna tawh amah phat unla, khausai lasaknate le tamngai tawh amah phat un.
verses.5: Daltuahte tawh amah phat unla, nakpi takin a ging daltuahte tawh amah phat un.
verses.6: Husang thei khempeuh in Topa phat un. Topa phat un.
